==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Redden
<hw>Red"den</hw> <pr>(r?d"d'n)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Reddened</conjf> <pr>(-d'nd)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. &
vb. n.</pos> <conjf>Reddening</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[From
<er>Red</er>, <pos>a.</pos>]</ety> <def>To make red or somewhat red; to
give a red color to.</def>⟦br⟧
