<p><ent>Redden</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Redden
<hw>Red"den</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To grow or become red; to
blush.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Appius <qex>reddens</qex> at each word you speak.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He no sooner saw that her eye glistened and her cheek
<qex>reddened</qex> than his obstinacy was at once subbued.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir W. SCott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reddendum</ent>⟦br⟧
